    "description": "你将在主游戏中扮演的第一个神是科尔努诺斯，以此迈出神灵角色的第一步。在今年夏天主游戏推出之前，学习从海中升起陆地、为你的追随者建立定居点、向一波又一波的入侵者降下火焰，并回应你追随者的祈祷。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325900/extras/076b4e09c954aebb0b1247143180c871.avif?t=1712494975\" width=616 height=165 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325900/extras/0d122ab3fb8af2d4bbd0af1271f38409.poster.avif?t=1712494975\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325900/extras/0d122ab3fb8af2d4bbd0af1271f38409.webm?t=1712494975\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325900/extras/0d122ab3fb8af2d4bbd0af1271f38409.mp4?t=1712494975\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在海上升起陆地，为你的追随者建造定居点，并为他们提供手段，获取繁荣发展所需的资源。随着你发现更多先进的建筑和战略，从平凡的起点扩展为拥有农场、工厂、防御工事等等的庞大岛链。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>为你的牌组收获卡牌</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325900/extras/ba07327f9f2f9c70b31d2fcd15d18ad4.poster.avif?t=1712494975\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325900/extras/ba07327f9f2f9c70b31d2fcd15d18ad4.webm?t=1712494975\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325900/extras/ba07327f9f2f9c70b31d2fcd15d18ad4.mp4?t=1712494975\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在大量卡牌和圣物中找到强大的协同作用，以克服途中的挑战。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325900/extras/1d2365ad5961c9c1a2965e88375de64a.avif?t=1712494975\" width=616 height=165 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325900/extras/022652fa099efc7d32b5d3da0ddba317.poster.avif?t=1712494975\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325900/extras/022652fa099efc7d32b5d3da0ddba317.webm?t=1712494975\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325900/extras/022652fa099efc7d32b5d3da0ddba317.mp4?t=1712494975\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>你能在这些毁灭的岛屿上生存下来吗？你将面临越来越多的挑战，因为一波又一波的入侵者和强大的头目试图破坏你所有的辛勤工作，把你的定居点变成废墟，并粉碎任何敢于挡路的追随者。从你的失败汲取教训，完善你的战略，以取得胜利。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325900/extras/55ab365aa0e3947d4c9949fbf597c81e.avif?t=1712494975\" width=616 height=165 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325900/extras/14dd72fe60340d8d39e39903e0c4c080.poster.avif?t=1712494975\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325900/extras/14dd72fe60340d8d39e39903e0c4c080.webm?t=1712494975\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325900/extras/14dd72fe60340d8d39e39903e0c4c080.mp4?t=1712494975\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>发现科尔努诺斯所拥有的独特神力，带领你的文明走向胜利。 <br><br><br>从抢先体验开始，主游戏将具有以下功能：<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>3个具有不同玩法、美学和能力的文明和神 <br></li><li>超过250张独特的卡牌 <br></li><li>超过20个独特的敌人和10个头目 <br></li><li>15个提升关卡 <br></li><li>超过30个圣物和诅咒，确保每次游戏都有不同的感觉<br></li><li>好友排行榜，让你可以与好友争夺最高分<br></li><li>创造模式，以建立你自己的场景或只是建造一个和平的定居点</li></ul>",
